---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';

const pageTitle = `Events | ${SITE_TITLE}`;
const pageDescription = 'Upcoming Stride City Run Club events, race meetups, and team outings.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<main>
			<section class="events-hero">
				<div class="container">
					<p class="eyebrow">Upcoming Events</p>
					<h1>Run with Stride City</h1>
					<p class="lede">
						From weekly miles to race-day meetups, this is where we share the events Stride City Run Club is showing up for together.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="events-list">
				<div class="container">
					<article class="event-card">
						<div class="event-card-header">
							<p class="event-kicker">Team Event</p>
							<h2>Run the South</h2>
						</div>

						<p>
							Stride City Run Club is putting together a team for <strong>Run the South Half Marathon, 10K &amp; 5K</strong>, one of Charlotte's summer race events at McAlpine Creek Park. Known as <strong>The Hottest Half</strong>, the race includes multiple distance options across a two-day format, including a Friday evening 5K and Saturday morning 10K and Half Marathon.
						</p>

						<div class="event-details" aria-label="Run the South event details">
							<div>
								<span>5K</span>
								<strong>Friday, June 19, 2026 at 6:15 PM</strong>
							</div>
							<div>
								<span>Half Marathon</span>
								<strong>Saturday, June 20, 2026 at 7:00 AM</strong>
							</div>
							<div>
								<span>10K</span>
								<strong>Saturday, June 20, 2026 at 7:30 AM</strong>
							</div>
							<div>
								<span>Location</span>
								<strong>McAlpine Creek Park, 8711 Monroe Rd, Charlotte, NC 28212</strong>
							</div>
							<div>
								<span>Club plan</span>
								<strong>Stride City team meetup</strong>
							</div>
							<div>
								<span>Race options</span>
								<strong>5K, 10K, Half Marathon, and challenge options</strong>
							</div>
						</div>

						<h3>Why this race?</h3>
						<p>
							Run the South is a great fit for Stride City because the course is described as fast and flat, with a route through mostly shaded greenways and wide open gravel paths. Whether you are chasing a PR, trying a new distance, or just looking for a fun race-day atmosphere with familiar faces, this is a strong summer goal race for the club.
						</p>

						<h3>Join the Stride City team</h3>
						<p>
							Register for the distance that works best for you, then look for the Stride City Run Club team option when signing up. As race day gets closer, we will share meetup details, team timing, and any packet pickup or pre-race plans.
						</p>

						<h3>What to expect</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Run the Friday 5K, the Saturday 10K, the Saturday Half Marathon, or one of the challenge options.</li>
							<li>Wear your Stride City gear if you have it, or bright colors so the team is easy to spot.</li>
							<li>Bring water and plan for summer heat.</li>
							<li>All paces are welcome. Come to race, run, walk, cheer, volunteer, or support the team.</li>
						</ul>
					</article>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.events-hero {
		padding: 5em 1.5em 4em;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.92), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.72));
		color: #fff;
	}

	.events-hero h1 {
		margin: 0 0 0.35em;
		font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		line-height: 1;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.eyebrow,
	.event-kicker {
		margin: 0 0 0.5em;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.lede {
		max-width: 680px;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
	}

	.events-list {
		padding: 4em 1.5em;
		background: #fff;
	}

	.event-card {
		padding: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 2.5em);
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		border-radius: 18px;
		box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.event-card-header {
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}

	.event-card h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.event-card p,
	.event-card li {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
	}

	.event-details {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1em;
		margin: 2em 0;
	}

	.event-details div {
		padding: 1em;
		border-radius: 14px;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
	}

	.event-details span {
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
	}

	.event-details strong {
		display: block;
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}

	.event-card h3 {
		margin-top: 1.75em;
		font-size: 1.35rem;
	}

	.event-card ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.2em;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.event-details {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
